  "title": "Chilled Shattering Middle-Eastern Eggplant Baba Ghanoush",
  "description": "A rich, creamy, and refreshing dip that shatters in your mouth. Perfect for a date night.",
  "cuisine": "Middle Eastern",
  "diet": [
