      "amount": "1 tsp"
    }
  ],
  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 400°F (200°C) and roast the eggplant for 30-40 minutes, or until the skin is charred and collapsed.",
    "Let the eggplant cool, then peel off the skin, chop it into large chunks, and puree in a blender until smooth.",
    "Transfer the eggplant puree to a large bowl and stir in the ground nut oil, roasted garlic, Kalamata olives, and bhuna sauce.",
    "Season with salt and black pepper, then refrigerate for at least 30 minutes to allow the flavors to meld.",
    "Just before serving, garnish with chopped fresh parsley and serve chilled."
  ],
